						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,1637128)"></a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/snowshoe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1354154); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1354154&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610183137" alt="Snowshoe" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1354154)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/snowshoe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1354154); return false;" >Snowshoe</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1354588157 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">04 Dec 2012 02:29</span>
